# Supabase (required for auth + shared library)
# Get these from your Supabase project: Settings > API
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Optional (for server-side admin tasks only; NEVER put real service key in browser bundles)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=...

# Notes:
# - After filling, copy to .env.local (gitignored)
# - Also create a "comics" Storage bucket (Public) in Supabase Dashboard for cover/panel images of public comics.
# - Configure OAuth providers (Google etc.) in Supabase Authentication > Providers.
# - Run the SQL schema from DESIGN-supabase-auth.md in the SQL Editor.
# - First-chapter-free + coin spend use server-protected paths.
